#: ../../../dev/gitwash/dot2_dot3.rst:5
msgid "Two and three dots in difference specs"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../dev/gitwash/dot2_dot3.rst:7
msgid "Thanks to Yarik Halchenko for this explanation."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../dev/gitwash/dot2_dot3.rst:9
msgid ""
"Imagine a series of commits A, B, C, D...  Imagine that there are two "
"branches, *topic* and *main*.  You branched *topic* off *main* when *main* "
"was at commit 'E'.  The graph of the commits looks like this::"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../dev/gitwash/dot2_dot3.rst:14
msgid ""
"     A---B---C topic\n"
"     /\n"
"D---E---F---G main"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../dev/gitwash/dot2_dot3.rst:18
msgid "Then::"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../dev/gitwash/dot2_dot3.rst:20
msgid "git diff main..topic"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../dev/gitwash/dot2_dot3.rst:22
msgid ""
"will output the difference from G to C (i.e. with effects of F and G), "
"while::"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../dev/gitwash/dot2_dot3.rst:25
msgid "git diff main...topic"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../dev/gitwash/dot2_dot3.rst:27
msgid ""
"would output just differences in the topic branch (i.e. only A, B, and C)."
msgstr ""
